data.description: ASK US how to get 5.875% RATE on this beautiful villa in Boynton Beach. First year get 3.875%! Call us today.   It has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, all with laminate floors. The living areas are comfortable and great for having friends over or spending time with family. The kitchen has nice stainless-steel appliances and lots of storage space. Washer and dryer in the unit. Brand new A/C.  Outside, there's a private covered patio that's perfect for chilling out. The house is in the Santa Cruz gated community, in a really nice neighborhood close to schools, parks, and stores. It's a great chance to own a home in this awesome community. FHA approved! Call to see it today!
